data.description:
Must see McKinney one-story ranch with acreage. Country lifestyle with city access. Located on 1.4 acre lot in a peaceful, rural setting. Scenic and
quaint but close to every convenience. Open floor plan with formal large living room and dining room. Kitchen with plenty of counter space & island open to family room with WB fireplace. Floorplan separates 3 bedrooms from primary suite with TWO walk-in closet & en-suite bathroom that includes jetted soaking tub and free standing shower. Covered front porch, handicap accessible back deck overlooking tree lined property complete with a stocked pond! Zone so that no one will build behind you! Property has a large 800 square foot enclosed building that can be used for business,
mancave or workshop. Additional 2 covered 2 car carport. This property truly has it all, spacious layout, charming features, & ample space for all of your hobbies and interests. It is a must-see for anyone looking for a peaceful, rural retreat.
